That&#39;s interesting.
Is a non-standard METHOD better than an ambiguous use of a standard METHOD?

-Solomon

On Thu, Jun 25, 2009 at 5:28 PM, Bill de hOra &lt;bill@...&gt; wrote:

&gt;
